description: Boozed-up Jamie-Lee McCabe, 30, from nearby Kensington, was filmed by her brother Luke Peffer as the pair rode up the escalator inside Flemington racecourse.

title: Irate voter slams Stephen Colbert for claiming he doesn't exist
description: In a monologue last week on The Late Show, Colbert mocked Republican candidate Tudor Dixon for a story she shared in her recent debate with incumbent Governor Gretchen Whitmer.

title: Cassius Turvey's best friend pays tribute to the 'beautiful boy with a big heart and big dreams'
description: Vision of Cassius Turvey's best friend taking to the stage at a vigil in Perth this week was posted on social media, where she said the 15-year-old was 'a best friend to everyone'.

title: WA: Truck carrying mining blasting material ERUPTS - truckie miraculously walks away
description: A road train carrying tonnes of mining blasting material caught fire and exploded, sending a mushroom cloud of hazardous smoke into the sky.

title: Traditional TV beats streaming ratings as Netflix overnight viewer numbers revealed for first time
description: Netflix might be the top streaming service but new figures reveal traditional TV attracts just as many - and often a lot more - viewers for individual shows.

title: NSW floods: Sydney dads Bob Chahine and Ghosn Ghosn swept away in Boorowa causeway incident
description: Two men missing in NSW's flood crisis have been identified as dads from Sydney. The pair were in the back of a ute when it was swept off a causeway and into raging waters.

title: GPs want to work 9-5 and be like people in 'most other jobs' so they can devote time to family
description: GPs are calling for their hours to be cut to 9am-5pm.The family doctors, who earn an average of £111,900 a year, say it is unfair to expect them to start earlier or finish later than 'most other jobs'.

title: Delaying cap on social care costs would be 'cruel and wrong', says economist who designed policy
description: Architect of the Government's flagship social care cap Sir Andrew Dilnot yesterday warned ministers it would be 'cruel and just wrong' to delay its implementation.

title: Body of American killed while fighting in Ukraine being held amid possible war crimes investigation
description: An American family who has been waiting to receive their son's body back after he died fighting in Ukraine says his remains are now being held pending a possible war crimes investigation.

title: Last Christmas post for the Queen as Royal Mail release stamps featuring late monarch's silhouette
description: The set of six art deco-style stamps focus on key moments from the Nativity story, and each bears an outline of the late monarch for the last time in more than 50 years.
